        { lines: ["I'm grateful for every shared experience that has woven our lives together, {{receiverName}}.", "From childhood adventures to adult conversations, from moments of laughter to times of serious reflection.", "Every experience has been a thread in the tapestry of our relationship.", "These memories aren't just pleasant recollections—they're the substance of who we've become together.", "I wouldn't change a single moment of our shared history.", "Thank you for creating such a rich and meaningful story with me."] },
        { lines: ["As we part, I want to encourage you to continue being the exceptional man you are, {{receiverName}}.", "Keep loving others with the generosity and authenticity that defines you.", "Keep standing for justice and truth, even when it requires courage.", "Keep growing and learning, always striving to become the best version of yourself.", "Keep being the kind of person others can look to for guidance and inspiration.", "The world desperately needs people like you, and I'm honored that you're my brother."] },
        { lines: ["I must acknowledge that leaving you is one of the most difficult things I've ever had to do, {{receiverName}}.", "Not because it's wrong, but because it means saying goodbye to someone who has been essential to my life.", "You've been my confidant, my advisor, my source of strength and stability.", "The thought of no longer having your daily presence feels overwhelming and heartbreaking.", "But I know that what we've built together is stronger than any distance that separates us.", "Our love and connection will endure because they're based on something deeper than physical proximity."] },
        { lines: ["I want to thank you for demonstrating what unconditional love truly means, {{receiverName}}.", "Through my failures and successes, my weaknesses and strengths, you've loved me consistently.", "You've shown me that true love isn't based on perfection but on choice and commitment.", "That understanding has shaped my capacity to love others and to accept love from them.", "It's given me a model for what all meaningful relationships should aspire to be.", "Thank you for that life-changing gift that will influence every relationship in my future."] },
        { lines: ["As I step into this new chapter, I carry with me all the wisdom you've imparted about living well, {{receiverName}}.", "Your lessons about integrity will guide my ethical decisions.", "Your example of loyalty will influence how I treat my commitments to others.", "Your demonstration of compassion will shape how I respond to those in need.", "You've given me a roadmap for navigating life with honor and purpose.", "Thank you for being such an extraordinary teacher through both your words and your actions."] },
        { lines: ["This goodbye is filled with both sorrow and gratitude, {{receiverName}}.", "Sorrow for the loss of your immediate presence and constant companionship.", "But overwhelming gratitude for having experienced such a profound and meaningful brotherhood.", "Not everyone is blessed with the kind of relationship we've shared.", "I consider myself incredibly fortunate to have had you as my brother.", "That gratitude will comfort me through the pain of separation."] },
        { lines: ["I need you to promise me that you'll treat yourself with the same care and respect you've shown others, {{receiverName}}.", "Be patient with your own growth and gentle with your imperfections.", "Pursue your goals with the confidence that comes from knowing your worth.", "Choose relationships with people who see and appreciate your value.", "Remember that you deserve the same loyalty and love you've given so generously.", "Take care of yourself because you're precious to me and to everyone who truly knows you."] },
        { lines: ["As we approach this farewell, I want you to know that you've surpassed every hope I could have had for a brother, {{receiverName}}.", "You've been more supportive than I dared expect, more loyal than I thought possible.", "You've given me more love, understanding, and encouragement than I ever imagined receiving.", "You've shown me what brotherhood can be when it's lived with intention and authentic care.", "I couldn't have designed a better brother if I had the power to create one.", "Thank you for exceeding every expectation and blessing my life beyond measure."] },
        { lines: ["I'm departing with a heart overflowing with love and a mind filled with precious memories, {{receiverName}}.", "Every moment we've shared has shaped the person I've become.", "Every lesson you've taught will influence the choices I make going forward.", "Every act of love you've shown will guide how I love others in the future.", "You've given me more than memories—you've given me a foundation for living well.", "I'll carry you with me always, not as a weight but as a source of strength and inspiration."] },
        { lines: ["{{receiverName}}, as I say this difficult goodbye, I want you to know that being your brother has been the greatest honor of my life.", "You've shown me the depths of love, the meaning of loyalty, and the power of authentic connection.", "You've taught me about character, integrity, and what it means to be a man of principle.", "You've been my greatest teacher, my most faithful friend, and my most treasured family member.", "Though saying goodbye breaks my heart, I'm grateful beyond words for the privilege of having been your brother.", "Thank you for everything you are and everything you've given me—I love you more than words can express."] }
