        { lines: ["{{receiverName}}, I want you to carry this truth with you as you go: you are loved, you are valued, and you matter deeply.", "Your life has meaning and purpose that extend beyond what you can see or measure in this moment.", "You make a difference in the world and in the lives of people who know you, including mine.", "Don't let distance or transition make you question your worth or your significance.", "You're important, you're valuable, and the world is better because you're in it.", "Hold onto that truth when things get hard, when you feel alone, when you wonder if you made the right choice."] },
        { lines: ["I want to commit to you that I'll keep our connection alive through intentional communication and effort, {{receiverName}}.", "I'll call regularly, text frequently, send care packages, plan visits—whatever it takes to maintain our bond.", "I won't assume you know I'm thinking of you—I'll tell you explicitly and remind you often of your importance to me.", "I'll make you a priority, not an afterthought, and I'll invest in our relationship despite the inconvenience of distance.", "And I'll need you to do the same: to stay engaged, to communicate openly, to make time for our relationship.", "Together, we can keep this bond strong, healthy, and vibrant regardless of physical separation."] },
        { lines: ["{{specialMemory}} will remind me during difficult moments of separation that our relationship is worth every effort to maintain, {{receiverName}}.", "That moment represents what we are to each other and why fighting for this connection matters so much.", "When maintaining our relationship feels hard or when I'm tempted to let distance create emotional separation, I'll remember that moment.", "It will motivate me to pick up the phone, to send that text, to book that flight, to do whatever it takes to stay close.", "That memory is a gift that will keep me committed to our brotherhood even when it requires sacrifice and intentional effort.", "Thank you for creating moments worth remembering and a relationship worth fighting for across any distance."] },
        { lines: ["As we say our goodbyes, I want you to know that I see you, {{receiverName}}—really see you.", "I see your strength and your vulnerability, your confidence and your doubts, your courage and your fears.", "I see who you are beneath the surface, and I love all of it—the polished and the rough, the certain and the questioning.", "That seeing creates a knowing that distance can't erase and time can't diminish.", "You're known by me, and that knowing is a gift I hope brings you comfort when you feel alone or misunderstood.", "Go forward knowing that someone truly sees you, knows you, and loves you exactly as you are."] },
        { lines: ["I want to release you to this next adventure with freedom, not guilt; with excitement, not obligation; with joy, not sorrow, {{receiverName}}.", "My sadness about your departure is about me, not about you—don't carry it as a burden or let it diminish your joy.", "I'm genuinely happy for you and excited about this opportunity, even though I'm sad for myself about the separation.", "Those feelings can coexist—I can be sad for me and happy for you simultaneously without contradiction.", "So please, go with a light heart, free from guilt or worry about those you're leaving behind.", "We'll be fine, and more importantly, we want you to be free to fully embrace what's ahead without emotional baggage."] },
        { lines: ["{{receiverName}}, I'm confident that this goodbye, as painful as it is, is part of a bigger story that we can't see yet.", "Sometimes separation serves purposes we don't understand in the moment but will appreciate with hindsight.", "Perhaps this time apart will deepen our appreciation for each other, strengthen our bond, or prepare us for what's ahead.", "I choose to trust that there's meaning in this moment even when I can't see it clearly right now.", "Let's both believe that our story together is far from over and that this goodbye is just one chapter in a much longer tale.", "I'm excited to see how this season of separation shapes us and where our journey together leads next."] },
        { lines: ["As I prepare to let you go, I'm filled with gratitude that overwhelms any sadness, {{receiverName}}.", "The blessing of having you as my brother far outweighs the pain of this temporary separation.", "I'd rather experience this goodbye than never have had our relationship in the first place.", "What we've shared has been worth every moment, and this farewell doesn't diminish that value one bit.", "I'm grateful for every memory, every conversation, every shared experience that has shaped our brotherhood.", "Thank you for being my brother, for making my life better through your presence, and for creating a bond worth grieving when we part."] }
